{"type": "article", "id": 19421, "title": "玻璃瓶吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-21T07:40:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071223524PmXoipnIYcwxyZF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t保加利亚的设计师 Iskren Marinov 带来了这盏有金属感的吊灯，用一块黑色的木板串起了 4 个玻璃果酱瓶。玻璃瓶里装有钨丝灯，上面连接了 4 根红色的电线，但在玻璃瓶里和电线上都故意保留了黑色的斑点，而不是常见的干净透明，有种很酷的原始质感，适合放在酒吧的环境中。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459237aZJrq9fhVSHgoM5.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145924YAVCDMfdzIWiu45n.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145925gZKa7L5GIMJitRsm.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145925FqzBSRETKCQdW2yZ.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}